{"tid":2291831,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"求問各高人：原來唔係個個啱用毛筆掛架催旺文昌讀書？","createTime":"2020-11-19T05:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T09:35:17.000Z","uid":340524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43933a1169dd2aa09d190dcdf6edbe21be36cca3","tid":2291831,"uid":340524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"條問題可能有啲基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為提供lihkg其他高人啲玄空理論基礎自學緊...但想問<br />\n<br />\n例如己卯丁卯庚申，城牆土命，好金土忌水火木（可能我錯，五行嗰啲真係咩都唔識要學返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n間屋坐北朝南，咁揀咗東北位擺四枝毛筆加掛架，想催旺文昌考試讀書好啲，但feel落個人好似有啲攰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後搵番話四綠係屬木，可能撞咗本身八字金克木唔知關唔關事。<br />\n<br />\n當然明白呢啲嘢應該搵專業師傅上門睇但怕驚動屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（佢哋唔太鍾意風水，但唔會反對擺啲嘢裝飾咁擺）。所以希望喺度簡略問返：<br />\n<br />\n（i) 如果命好金土，係咪擺四枝毛筆旺文昌邊個方位都唔啱？要用其他咩金水局果啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（ii）如果擺少啲毛筆個數唔用49 用其他會唔會好啲？<br />\n<br />\n（iii) 其實generally有冇得學自己八字同風水擺設屬性有冇關事？之前見高人係度推介咗玄空大廈風水論，有冇其他推介係入門書籍可以學返嚟？（當然明白如果跟啱師傅一定最有效，但想打一打好個基礎先）<br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9336613c742f96fe78e0516d3e60416a453057dc","tid":2291831,"uid":36105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"擺富貴竹啦"},{"pid":"e18b85f23cecce552420fb2b10ac678935809aea","tid":2291831,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"自己俾心機專心啦"},{"pid":"8139f60fe79426b28aded24444d15ce8b397e23d","tid":2291831,"uid":366281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"專心讀書啦，你唔好好讀擺乜都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2820898e352818ef8d2a479179e9c03781df6f","tid":2291831,"uid":340524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"多謝眾巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身個科都要成日讀書或者journal 但係係自己間房不能冇乜精神專心到 點知跟網上話座椅要有靠山 橫樑壓頂可以靠掛葫蘆／錢化煞之後真係覺得讀書易咗入腦 所以想睇下有無得讀書運果度再好啲（成日tutor改essay爛grade，然後問返佢哋對照番啲criteria／tutor 比嘅suggestion話點解做到晒都無a/b range, 佢哋又有時唔係好答得出，甚至有時話純粹整體感覺麻麻地，然後次次跟晒cm又係下次都衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 所以不得不覺得似係關風水運勢事 想至少可以一分耕耘一分收穫返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，明明自問啲嘢都算明同有努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0814e00056f060ba15ebd9b81160abd19a65ca75","tid":2291831,"uid":340524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9336613c742f96fe78e0516d3e60416a453057dc","tid":2291831,"uid":36105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"擺富貴竹啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"謝巴（or 絲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1d742338bd72442ccf2e9758bd43708ca01870","tid":2291831,"uid":268450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"962730c7ece25e9cf1be3b14d93c2b3146fd94d1","tid":2291831,"uid":340524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1d742338bd72442ccf2e9758bd43708ca01870","tid":2291831,"uid":268450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"真心多謝師傅指路 信命自己都會／要努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj